  "curation": {
    "synopsis": "Caleb Cursebound, the Underhive's self-declared ninth-most-dangerous man, is hiding with Iktomi after bringing down a noble-house tyrant. Hope's End should be nowhere enough to disappear, but the mining settlement is trapped under a brutal House Orlock gang and desperate for a champion. Caleb promises more than he can safely give, while drink, paranoia and an old grudge close in around both fugitives. A rough-edged redemption novella about a braggart forced into heroism and hunted by the life he keeps outrunning.",
